      <title>胡塞叛军誓言在美国、英国领导的最新袭击后发起新的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/yemen-based-houthis-vow-retaliation-to-us-uk-airstrikes</link>
